name: CASH
description: money that can be used to buy an asset in a transaction immediately

name: IMMEDIATE_CONSUMABLE
description: finished product or service that is consumed immediately by a person

name: LONG_TERM_CONSUMABLE
description: finished product or service that depreciates over time
column3: can be bought by person or company--aka CAPEX

name: RAW_MATERIAL
description: an input for another asset of another asset type such as consumable

name: PROPERTY
description: property like land or a house or both
